%1.name
=======
- pick up the ageis, this will give you a new action button
- Do not cast any abilities while channeling the ageis
- [ragnarok] cast, you need to use ageis at the last moment
    - it is directional, face the shield against the boss, everyone should
        go behind your shield
- [savage blade] does a lot of damage, use defensive
- [ageis of aggramar] cast, get behind boss to damage
- after [ageis of aggramar] cast, the boss throws the ageis, go find it
- [felblaze rush] cast charges random player and does aoe 
- focus down Flame of Woe elmeentals
